import { Facebook, Instagram } from '@material-ui/icons'
import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Contact>
                <Address>Chamisal Vineyard 7525 Orcutt Road San Luis Obispo, CA 93401</Address>
                <Number>210-24-63-127</Number>
                <Email>info@chamisalvineyards.com</Email>
            </Contact>
            <Logo>
                <Name>CHAMISAL VINEYARDS</Name>
                <Social>
                    <Insta><Instagram /></Insta>
                    <Face><Facebook /></Face>
                </Social>
            </Logo>
            <Links>
                <Title>RESOURCES</Title>
                <Link>Store Locator</Link>
                <Link>Trade & Media</Link>
                <Link>Shipping</Link>
                <Link>Privacy Policy</Link>
                <Link>Terms</Link>
                <Link>Community</Link>
                <Link>Sustainability</Link>
                <Link>Careers</Link>
            </Links>
        </Container>
    )
}

const Container = styled.div`
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    margin-top: 50px;
`

const Contact = styled.div`
    flex: 1;
`
const Address = styled.span``
const Number = styled.span``
const Email = styled.span``
const Logo = styled.div`
    flex: 2;
`

const Name = styled.h2``
const Social = styled.span``
const Insta = styled.span``
const Face = styled.span``
const Links = styled.div`
    flex: 1;
`

const Title = styled.p``
const Link = styled.a``

export default Footer
